<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,621,900]" pageId="5" pageNumber="482">
This species was described from several specimens collected in the Chian Rai province in 
<collectingCountry box="[1194,1297,765,791]" name="Thailand" pageId="5" pageNumber="482">Thailand</collectingCountry>
. For the first time, we here report it from 
<collectingCountry box="[464,573,802,828]" name="Myanmar" pageId="5" pageNumber="482">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
and from the vicinity of 
<collectingRegion box="[849,984,801,827]" country="Thailand" name="Chiang Mai" pageId="5" pageNumber="482">Chiang Mai</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[994,1097,801,827]" name="Thailand" pageId="5" pageNumber="482">Thailand</collectingCountry>
. The specimens were attracted to pheromone lures in late morning; the one from 
<collectingRegion box="[725,859,837,863]" country="Thailand" name="Chiang Mai" pageId="5" pageNumber="482">Chiang Mai</collectingRegion>
in subtropical rain forest, the two specimens from 
<collectingCountry box="[151,260,874,900]" name="Myanmar" pageId="5" pageNumber="482">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
in monsoonal forest along a creek bed.
</paragraph>
